      "review_summary": "The PR replaces selected Vydra, xAI, Runway, Pixverse, DeepInfra, Together, ElevenLabs, Microsoft Foundry, and Microsoft success-response `response.json()` calls with direct `readResponseWithLimit` plus `JSON.parse` calls using 1 MiB caps.\n\nPR surface: Source +87. Total +87 across 12 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. PR-head source inspection shows parse-breaking constants at DeepInfra and Vydra speech, plus too-narrow helper signatures passed to a full-Response bounded reader; I did not run tests because this review is read-only.",
